item.title: CVE-2016-4902|2024-08-06T00:46:39.972Z -- japan%20agency%20for%20local%20authority%20information%20systems -- the%20public%20certification%20service%20for%20individuals%20%22the%20jpki%20user%27s%20software%20%28for%20windows%207%20and%20later%29%22
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in The Public Certification Service for Individuals "The JPKI user's software (for Windows 7 and later)" Ver3.0.1 and earlier, The Public Certification Service for Individuals "The JPKI user's software (for Windows Vista)" Ver3.0.1 and earlier and The Public Certification Service for Individuals "The JPKI user's software" Ver2.6 and earlier allows remote attackers to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
